        The processor definition for Getter. Tries to obtain a value through a getter method inside the provided Event instance. If no method exists null is returned. This processor is performed in a EventStage.POPULATE stage, making it the first available option to provide the object value. It is possible there is another annotation processed before this if it is in the same stage, in which case the processor respects the value of Provided.overrideExisting().
